Que:-How To Handle drop	down elements with select tag..??

Ans:-	we can handle drop down with the help of Select class First we have to create the object of 
		Select class by passing the WebElement Instance...

				Select sel = new Select(WebElement Instance);

		Then by using that object we can handle the drop down..
		To select options from drop	down we can use three methods...
		
		sel.selectByIndex()  			........ 	insert index integer
		sel.selectByValue()				........ 	insert value in string
		sel.selectByVisibleText()		........ 	insert visible text in string
		
		
		To capture the selected options we use "getFirstSelectedOption()" method and the return type of this method is WebElement